2(f) does not cover transfer of a permit.","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In subsection (b), the word “adequate” is omitted as surplus.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
